00:01:12.950 --> 00:01:15.980
Professor Leon Lederman, a physicist,

00:01:15.980 --> 00:01:19.280
Nobel laureate, former
director of Fermilab,

00:01:19.280 --> 00:01:21.300
educator and author.

00:01:21.300 --> 00:01:23.640
I'm not gonna give you
