00:43:04.440 --> 00:43:07.315
And what's your first,
what's your feeling,

00:43:07.315 --> 00:43:08.915
when the first time?

00:43:08.915 --> 00:43:11.880
- Let me say, winning the Nobel Prize

00:43:11.880 --> 00:43:13.842
is something I recommend very highly.

00:43:13.842 --> 00:43:15.450
(audience laughs)

00:43:15.450 --> 00:43:17.423
It really is a lot of fun.

00:43:19.170 --> 00:43:20.003
This,

00:43:22.510 --> 00:43:25.900
probably as usual, it
happens late at night.

00:43:25.900 --> 00:43:27.253
You get a telephone call.

00:43:28.263 --> 00:43:31.970
I think in this particular
case or one very much like it,

00:43:31.970 --> 00:43:33.280
my wife had the phone

00:43:33.280 --> 00:43:36.860
and we sort of suspected
there would be an award.

00:43:36.860 --> 00:43:38.540
It was rumored and so on.

00:43:38.540 --> 00:43:42.697
And she got the telephone
call and she said to me,

00:43:42.697 --> 00:43:44.307
"We can't go to Sweden

00:43:44.307 --> 00:43:46.754
"because I have a dinner date that night."

00:43:46.754 --> 00:43:47.587
(audience laughs)

00:43:47.587 --> 00:43:48.750
And she handed me the phone.

00:43:48.750 --> 00:43:53.750
And she was kidding, of course. (laughs)

00:43:53.930 --> 00:43:57.140
So, I recommend winning
a prize very highly.

00:43:57.140 --> 00:43:58.390
It's a great thing to do.

