think, two experiences.

00:45:26.590 --> 00:45:29.620
First of all, I had a lab on
the 10th floor of Pupin, also.

00:45:29.620 --> 00:45:30.453
- Oh, yeah.

00:45:30.453 --> 00:45:32.683
- [Audience Member] But
I remember one morning,

00:45:34.220 --> 00:45:35.910
doing experiments, staying up at night

00:45:35.910 --> 00:45:37.760
