00:46:00.640 --> 00:46:01.960
- Well, it was a great department

00:46:01.960 --> 00:46:04.430
and having those people around was

00:46:06.343 --> 00:46:08.363
a fantastic experience.

00:46:09.420 --> 00:46:14.320
